{"tid":2051798,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"轟王冬勝撐港版國安法 英國議員甘文康致函滙豐：下議院極大擔憂","createTime":"2020-06-05T04:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T08:11:11.000Z","uid":70063,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9bed948e4c6fad1d0acf7b57286a4aee5939cf7f","tid":2051798,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/amcarmichaelMP/status/1268610013783707648?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FamcarmichaelMP%2Fstatus%2F1268610013783707648%3Fs%3D19&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=3471af9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FamcarmichaelMP%2Fstatus%2F1268610013783707648%3Fs%3D19&h=6ed3345d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/amcarmichaelMP/status/1268610013783707648?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n日前官媒、前特首梁振英批評滙豐未有支持「港版國安法」，滙豐隨即跪低，亞太區行政總裁王冬勝現身街站簽名支持國安法，事件引起英國政界強烈批評，指滙豐違背英國既定立場，引起了恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，英國議會香港問題小組主席Alistair Carmichael提到英國政府反對「港版國安法」，批評王冬勝支持削弱香港的自由和自治的法案。他在向滙豐CEO Noel Quinn致函指出，此舉引起下議院重大關注，指王冬勝行動或導致不穩定的商業環境，北京所威脅的行動破壞制度，對所有人都不利，並對滙豐與破壞規則和秩序的人結盟，感到擔憂。<br />\n<br />\n下議院領袖Jacob Rees-Mogg批評，滙豐立場更接近中國政府，而不是英國。執政黨保守黨議員Tom Tugendhat亦於Twitter上發帖，同時批評滙豐和同樣表態支持國案法的渣打，質疑兩機構為何支持專制國家鎮壓自由、破壞法治。Neil O'Brien更暗示英國人應轉用其他銀行。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐銀行駐倫敦發言人拒絕回應該社查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/UMKTPAPZJSJRWYSJ7YF5FEYJZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FUMKTPAPZJSJRWYSJ7YF5FEYJZA%2F&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EsQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=683259db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200605%2FUMKTPAPZJSJRWYSJ7YF5FEYJZA%2F&h=ad82b2d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/finance/20200605/UMKTPAPZJSJRWYSJ7YF5FEYJZA/</a>"},{"pid":"12026a3be92ef8bfe10affdbea1618870b2c483e","tid":2